This article is a memorandum issued by President Donald J. Trump. It delegates certain authorities under Section 1244(c) of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2018 to the Secretary of State, in coordination with the Secretary of the Treasury, the Secretary of Defense, the Secretary of Commerce, and the Director of National Intelligence. The memorandum states that these delegations of authority will also apply to any future public laws that have similar provisions. The Secretary of State is also authorized and directed to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.